{"tid":1128381,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普與Twitter CEO會面  投訴followers減少","createTime":"2019-04-27T18:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T09:18:47.000Z","uid":66271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9f1538836dc92e8ae23888d225522e699ec61f15","tid":1128381,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T18:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/donald-trump-jack-dorsey.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fdonald-trump-jack-dorsey.jpg&h=b523f57b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然已經做了總統這麼長時間，大家都知道美國總統Donald Trump特朗普仍然很愛玩Twitter，不時還會隔空發炮罵人。他最近與Twitter CEO Jack Dorsey等人會面，特朗普對於他突然少了一些Follower十分不滿，認為Jack專登玩嘢。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普認為Twitter CEO是因為政治因素，而把其Follower移除，特朗普稱無緣無故失去了近六千萬Follower令他不滿。不過，Jack立即解釋是因為公司政策，不時會移除一些SPAM或假戶口，就連Jack本身也會失去一些Follower。<br />\n<br />\n據稱有關會面由白宮提議，但白宮不願回應傳媒查詢。Twitter則指會面的重點議題，是在2020總統大選來到前，希望社交網絡的言論自由得到保障，也要避免再出現上次言論被人操控等情況。特朗普一直認為，網絡上有人針對他們，只是因為他們在社會上有一定的地位或權力，特朗普亦多次在公開場合，放口風威脅要管制互聯網。"},{"pid":"f4762ab490424d40fb4a1b1743b2b9d14c93c190","tid":1128381,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T19:03:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Twitter則指會面的重點議題，是在2020總統大選來到前，希望社交網絡的言論自由得到保障，<span style=\"color: red;\">也要避免再出現上次言論被人操控等情況</span>。</blockquote><br />\n小心中國網軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ti2gljctsS_e.wt_Tx3j.Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MjY0/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/f67b65cfebed823c651233941b4e9c4b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fti2gljctsS_e.wt_Tx3j.Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MjY0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Ff67b65cfebed823c651233941b4e9c4b&h=c4290822&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":